hom-fam-is-cov‚áĒis-strongly-segal
  : ‚ąÄ {ūĚď§} {A : Type ūĚď§}
    ‚Üí (‚ąÄ x ‚Üí is-covariant (őĽ a ‚Üí Hom A x a))
